<section id="selecttext">
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3147576" xml-lang="en-US"><ahelp hid=".">You can enable a selection cursor in a read-only text document or in the Help. Choose <menuitem>Edit - Select Text</menuitem> or open the context menu of a read-only document and choose <menuitem>Select Text</menuitem>. The selection cursor does not blink.</ahelp></paragraph>
